Class HashTable<K,V>

java.lang.Object
hashtable.HashTable<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - the type of keys maintained by this hash table.
V - the type of mapped values.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<HashTable.Entry<K,V>>
public class HashTable<K,V> extends Object implements Iterable<HashTable.Entry<K,V>>
A generic hash table implementation that maps keys to values.
